Rating: 3
Great base recipe, but made some changes: omitted carrots, substituted 2 c. chicken stock for 2 c. water, 1 can Great Northern beans for 1 can cannellini, and 1.5 TB dried ground sage for 2 tsp. fresh. Added: 2 cloves garlic, bay leaf, 1/3 c. white wine, pinch ground thyme. I topped each serving with a generous amt of fresh cracked black pepper and grated parmigiano-reggiano. Delish w/garlic bread! When I make this again, I will add more prosciutto and possibly a handful of elbow pasta to thicken it up.

